com.vincestyling.asqliteplus

Interface DBOperator<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the produced SQL statement. The caller would invoke its #toString() to take the final statement. Can be either a normal String which just the SQL or represented the SQL's Statement object.

    public interface DBOperator<T>
    This class used to producing a SQL statement by the given entity. Usually an INSERT||UPDATE||DELETE statement in a batch operation context.
    See Also:
    DBOverseer.executeBatch(java.util.List, DBOperator)
